    • Field Detail

      • lineCommentStart

        protected int lineCommentStart
        The line number for the initial (prefixing) comment. If no comment is present, this will be set to the same line number as the starting line number.

      • lineEnd

        protected int lineEnd
        The line number for the last line of the symbol declaration. This may be set to the same line number as the starting line number.

    • Constructor Detail

      • MibFileRef

        public MibFileRef()
        Creates a void MIB file reference. This is used when line numbers or file name isn't available, typically for symbols automatically created outside the loaded MIB (such as the OID root symbols).

      • MibFileRef

        Creates a new MIB file reference.
        Parameters:
        file - the file name
        line - the start line number
        column - the start column number
